#                               Output Discipline ref, /recover re-apply,
#                               collision guarantee
#   CLAUDE.md                -- §5 whitelist (4 keys + per-key exclusions)
#   skills/clickup/SKILL.md  -- --workspace flag + state-based read
#   skills/recover/SKILL.md  -- re-apply from 00-state.md
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
